library(estimatr)
test <- glm(populist ~ estsz + I(sclmeet + inprdsc + sclact) + male + agea + I(agea**2) + eduyrs + occup_level, ess %>% filter(self_emp10 == 0 & agea %in% 18:64 & cntry == 'IT'), family = binomial())
